Create a modern, professional developer portfolio as a responsive SPA using React (Next.js preferred).

The design should be clean, minimal, and slightly futuristic, with smooth animations and a strong focus on readability and hierarchy.

Sections required:

1. Hero Section
- Name: Guilherme Smith Dansiguer Rodrigues
- Title: Fullstack Developer | Database Specialist
- Short tagline: "Building reliable systems under pressure"
- CTA buttons: "View Projects", "Contact"

2. About Me
- Summary describing experience with backend, databases, and critical incident handling
- Highlight strong SQL expertise and real-world production experience
- Mention automation and performance optimization

3. Skills
- Grouped sections:
  - Backend: Node.js, PHP
  - Frontend: React, JavaScript
  - Database: MariaDB, SQL (advanced)
  - DevOps: Docker, Linux, ShellScript
- Display as badges or cards

4. Projects (IMPORTANT)
- Fetch dynamically from GitHub API:
  https://api.github.com/users/YOUR_USERNAME/repos
- Show only relevant projects (filter out forks if possible)
- Each project card should include:
  - Name
  - Description
  - Main language
  - Link to repository
- Highlight top 4-6 projects visually

5. Experience
- Timeline style
- Focus on:
  - Database Technician (IXC Soft)
  - Implementation Consultant
  - Tech Support Leader
- Emphasize:
  - Incident response
  - Root cause analysis
  - Data consistency fixes
  - Automation impact

6. Education & Certifications
- Systems Information degree (in progress)
- Relevant courses (Docker, MySQL DBA, React)

7. Contact
- Email
- LinkedIn
- Simple contact form (optional)

Technical requirements:
- Use React.js
- bootstrap for styling
- Smooth scroll navigation
- Subtle animations (Framer Motion preferred)
- Dark mode default
- Fully responsive
- Clean component structure

Extra features (nice to have):
- Loading skeletons for GitHub data
- GitHub API caching
- SEO metadata
- Sticky navbar

Design direction:
- Professional but not boring
- Slightly bold tech aesthetic
- Avoid generic templates
- Prioritize clarity over decoration